# INSTRUCTION
# This program is used for crawl Chinese-Russia sentence pair for tmxmall
# This project provides an anonymous crawler for web pages.
# For some resons, server will ban web crawler (include ban ip/refuse connections) 
# Use a framework Scrapy
#
# To avoid been banned of the server, we use the following techs : 
#   
#   1) Forbid the cookies
#
#   2) Delay the time between the request 
#   
#   3) Random rotate the user agent of each request
#
#   4) Random rotate the proxy ip of the client 
#
# Tutorial :
#
# step_1 : Run script in IP_Detect/python_candidates.py  
# step_2 : Run script in IP_Detect/python_detect.py
# step_3 : Run script in Russia/scrapy crawl pages
# step_4 : Run script in Russia/scrapy crawl russia
#
